{"tid":1488014,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"想問香港淨番咩KOL/YouTuber","createTime":"2019-08-19T13:21:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-14T13:16:29.000Z","uid":134209,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"851b66cbc1c96c2812591227cf0bd24a85bdf57b","tid":1488014,"uid":134209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T13:21:44.000Z","msg":"見隔離post問淨番咩藝人<br />\n所以都好奇香港有咩KOL/ YouTuber係有內涵唔係淨係飲飲食食扮靚打機<br />\n<br />\n個人覺得藝人要支持真係唔係話咁易 咁當然做護旗手嗰啲就不能原諒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過KOL/ YouTuber就唔同 大部分自由身 講咩做咩好直接反映到自己係咩料<br />\n而香港人嘅支持都好直接影響佢地收入 所以真係想撐下啲黃底KOL/YouTuber 抵制死藍絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n拋磚引玉:<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">黃底</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大J</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V3cDTjg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV3cDTjg.png&h=d798ed33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第一個真係不得不說大J 身體力行走上前線 零gear食tg<br />\n仲要深入敵穴<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Flavia Wong</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OwW1Q6d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOwW1Q6d.png&h=06d2582d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n睇得出佢係個真黃絲唔係行出黎抽水打卡嗰種<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">臭藍絲</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Merry So</span></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tCLNMFh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtCLNMFh.png&h=af32f8f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之前八五屌人公開佢住嘅公屋密碼 不過之後道左歉 唔知大家點睇<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GZAmQ7y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGZAmQ7y.png&h=a09d5ad6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Sadelle</span></span><br />\n⼀<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JjXTHeu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJjXTHeu.png&h=0238b3cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n係IG度偽中立 譴責暴力 又係story share港人港地fb post 話條片值得深思<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n惹人非議之後又刪人comment block人account<br />\n撐佢嗰啲佢就唔del<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實呢個所謂KOL都7過幾獲嫁喇<br />\n之前係pinerest偷相扮自己旅行相係經典7事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一時間未諗起其他 不過總之呢就<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">全面抵制所有藍絲!!!!</span></span>"},{"pid":"6e4f93b7fe501862611ce792f2ed2c6cf85faa1a","tid":1488014,"uid":134209,"like":1,"dislike":10,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T13:25:13.000Z","msg":"自膠 補番圖先<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VCurhRm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVCurhRm.png&h=38704440&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HOQBE4H.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHOQBE4H.png&h=18f223b0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9b99dc9775563020504aa4ee0b5fdd5a3de64306","tid":1488014,"uid":76632,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T13:28:06.000Z","msg":"白兵"},{"pid":"6ee0a96e3bf5614948b14a651c77fbb6e9eb7505","tid":1488014,"uid":61748,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T13:28:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6478869fd48039e2